//Installation//

Change the Directory to:

C:\Programme\Steam\steamapps\NAME\counter-strike source\

and take the downloaded folder named cstrike and Drag&Drop or Copy&Paste it into the CSS Root Folder.

You'r done !




How To Start:

Go ingame, open Console and write:

map ba_jail_stations

Press enter and you can play it.
